### Welcome in your blog!
By default it uses [Markdown Syntax](http://daringfireball.net/projects/markdown/syntax) in post body, and YAML to set blog metadata

This software is based on awesome [Mojolicious](http://mojolicio.us/) framework

if you use -- more -- in newline, part before will be considered summary and -- more -- will be removed from post, like that:
 -- more --

Yep just like that

have fun
